        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "] i.e. The Temple building. The next verse speaks of the enclosing framework of chambers. What was now finished was the portion for divine service.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
